{"tid":396194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬特列治踢頭領黃 紅軍迷轟不公","createTime":"2017-09-11T13:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:30:07.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a34b45390512410ac6d43d4ef4bf43ce385cc821","tid":396194,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rgZD6r3FPc5Ns%2Bl0aH1nmsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ddef07ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】紐卡素翼鋒馬特列治周日對史雲斯一戰的犯規動作，與周六利物浦的沙迪奧文尼有點兒相似，但前者只換來一面黃牌，令紅軍球迷深感不滿。<br />\n<br />\n周日紐卡素作客1:0小勝史雲斯的比賽，下半場開賽初段，紐卡素翼鋒馬特列治（Matt Ritchie）於一次爭奪控球權中，舉起右腳搶波，更衝向史雲斯後衛艾菲莫臣（Alfie Mawson），被球證吹罰。幸好雙方沒有完全接觸，而莫臣亦向球證示意自己並沒有大礙，最終是次犯規動作，為馬特列治帶來一面黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n不過，此事卻引來利物浦球迷的不滿，事緣紅軍周六作客曼城一戰，沙迪奧文尼與馬特列治的搶波動作相似，亦是舉腳過高，但文尼卻被球證摩斯以直紅驅逐離場，紅軍球迷紛紛在網上批評英超球證執法不一。<br />\n<br />\n網民@RichyRichynwa表示：「球證執法不統一，文尼紅牌，馬特列治因沒有傷及對手而黃牌，應該一視同仁，二人一起紅牌或一起黃牌。」另一位網民@StirkS85則說：「完全不統一的決定！兩者完全一樣的挑戰，但文尼紅牌，馬特列治則黃牌。」至於@Gaz5tevo就說：「我認為馬特列治都應該拿紅牌，兩者唯一分別就是艾達臣摩拉斯受傷，但艾菲莫臣則沒有。」"},{"pid":"9f9cee45146cbf6cadf9aec64c9fe75fda3f09e3","tid":396194,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"猁迷仲想講到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fca620e258fa500295b0b9b3e1ee74342238f89","tid":396194,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/211153_78036127416125c90f89ceb057776081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F211153_78036127416125c90f89ceb057776081.jpg&h=520d3bb5&s={SIZE}\" />又迫害我利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7499723f0f5023ac4d0ad5bf7caff4a5ef167c7b","tid":396194,"uid":18674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"猁迷玻璃心到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算紅左文尼都無所謂啦<br />\n黎緊果3場都係打弱隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a752437a38e64a1d28e8c8c22563d19760b2da7","tid":396194,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeae64d006e86f4a281793595f08a6eac0f3c85","tid":396194,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"47898f78d2dcb9c5009b634b1f3a6595d4282c0f","tid":396194,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> is被逼害"},{"pid":"45e219d0f49bfafba55d981ebeb7ec83e489aa8a","tid":396194,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"115bdbc2961bef04a3a50f4f8bba1d3ae26829ef","tid":396194,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ecc563d6a8f665bb32fca3c0c1798295cd2cbe","tid":396194,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2a0f9f1f007a1a386ad024f040e28e010d975a","tid":396194,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:57:27.00